passionate /ˈpæʃənɪt/

1. ADJ A passionate person has very strong feelings about something or a strong belief in something. 狂热的; 热诚的 

例： ...his passionate commitment to peace. …他对和平事业的狂热信奉。 

例： He is very passionate about the project. 他对这个项目非常热诚。 

2. passionately ADV 狂热地; 热诚地 

例： I am passionately opposed to the death penalty. 我强烈地反对死刑。 

3. ADJ A passionate person has strong romantic or sexual feelings and expresses them in their behaviour. 非常浪漫的; 性欲强的 

例： ...a beautiful, passionate woman of twenty-six. …一位美丽的、非常浪漫的26岁的妇女。 

4. passionately ADV 非常浪漫地; 性欲强地 

例： He was passionately in love with her. 他热恋着她。

